    <title>Mac下利用Hexo+Github搭建静态个人博客</title>
    <link href="http://xuhe0903.xyz/2018/10/02/Mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8Hexo-Github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>http://xuhe0903.xyz/2018/10/02/Mac下利用Hexo-Github搭建静态个人博客/</id>
    <published>2018-10-02T12:50:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-02T13:49:31.526Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h1><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/download/mac</a></p><h1 id="安装Node-js"><a href="#安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装Node.js"></a>安装Node.js</h1><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a></p><h1 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h1><h2 id="先创建一个用来存放Blog的文件夹，然后cd进这个目录"><a href="#先创建一个用来存放Blog的文件夹，然后cd进这个目录" class="headerlink" title="先创建一个用来存放Blog的文件夹，然后cd进这个目录"></a>先创建一个用来存放Blog的文件夹，然后cd进这个目录</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例如 <span class="built_in">cd</span> Desktop/hexo_blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="还是在这个目录，进行初始化"><a href="#还是在这个目录，进行初始化" class="headerlink" title="还是在这个目录，进行初始化"></a>还是在这个目录，进行初始化</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="配置ssh"><a href="#配置ssh" class="headerlink" title="配置ssh"></a>配置ssh</h1><h2 id="依次执行以下命令"><a href="#依次执行以下命令" class="headerlink" title="依次执行以下命令"></a>依次执行以下命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config –global user.name “name”</span><br><span class="line">git config –global user.eamil “emali”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的”name”和”emali”可以随便写</p><h2 id="创建ssh"><a href="#创建ssh" class="headerlink" title="创建ssh"></a>创建ssh</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “youremail@example.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="找到ssh生成的pub文件"><a href="#找到ssh生成的pub文件" class="headerlink" title="找到ssh生成的pub文件"></a>找到ssh生成的pub文件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后再输入<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">open .   注意，open后面有一个空格</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>用文本编辑器打开id_rsa.pub，将其内容复制到Github的setting里的deploy keys去，添加时title可留空。</p><h1 id="修改-config-yml文件"><a href="#修改-config-yml文件" class="headerlink" title="修改_config.yml文件"></a>修改_config.yml文件</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">repo: https://github.com/xxx/xxx.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>xxx为个人github的name<br>标题之类的，可以参考<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xuezhisdc/article/details/53130383" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/xuezhisdc/article/details/53130383</a></p><h2 id="本地预览博客"><a href="#本地预览博客" class="headerlink" title="本地预览博客"></a>本地预览博客</h2><p>输入以下命令<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在浏览器中打开<a href="http://localhost:4000即可" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000即可</a></p><h1 id="同步到GitHub"><a href="#同步到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="同步到GitHub"></a>同步到GitHub</h1><p>依次输入以下命令<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="撰写文章"><a href="#撰写文章" class="headerlink" title="撰写文章"></a>撰写文章</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new 文章标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="大功告成！"><a href="#大功告成！" class="headerlink" title="大功告成！"></a>大功告成！</h1><p>由于时间仓促，内容较为简陋，有时间会进行相应的补充！</p>]]></content>
    
